uk.co.strangeskies.utilities

Class Enumeration<S extends Enumeration<S>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.Enumeration<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - Self bounding on the type of the enumeration class.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Copyable<S>, Self<S>

    public class Enumeration<S extends Enumeration<S>>
extends Object
implements Self<S>
    A reimplementation of Java's Enum class, primarily for the purpose of facilitating enumerations with generics. This class should enforce most of the rules governing enum, including limiting instance creation to static initializer blocks. Unfortunately error detection of such problems is inevitably shifted to runtime rather than compile time.
